pizzle rot
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a disease of rams and wethers in the summer and autumn, affecting the sheath.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
